Abstaining:

Botswana, India, Kazakhstan, Namibia, Philippines, Sierra Leone

946. Amendment A/HRC/27/L.48 was rejected by 17 votes to 21, with 6 abstentions.[39]

947. At the same meeting, the representatives of Costa Rica and Ireland made statements in explanation of vote before the vote in relation to amendment A/HRC/27/L.49.

