949. Amendment A/HRC/27/L.49 was rejected by 16 votes to 21, with 7 abstentions.[40]

950. At the same meeting, the representative of Estonia made a statement in explanation of vote before the vote in relation to amendment A/HRC/27/L.50.

951. Also at the same meeting, at the request of the representatives of Brazil and Chile, a recorded vote was taken on amendment A/HRC/27/L.50. The voting was as follows:

