952. Amendment A/HRC/27/L.50 was rejected by 16 votes to 22, with 6 abstentions.[41]

953. At the same meeting, the representative of Austria made a statement in explanation of vote before the vote in relation to amendment A/HRC/27/L.51.

954. Also at the same meeting, at the request of the representatives of Brazil and Chile, a recorded vote was taken on amendment A/HRC/27/L.51. The voting was as follows:

In favour:

